d":214753,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東＝東家＝主塲＝我話事<br />\n所以就東行先<br />\n<br />\n至於其他就ＷＦＣ</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   你覺得有方向既「東」 先 定係 有「東家」個「東」 依個字先呢 ?"},{"pid":"26319847a6e7c1587b828bef6e1115ba648e4e44","tid":214753,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:48:13.000Z","msg":"點解要 上下左右<br />\n<br />\n唔可以<br />\n下上右左？"},{"pid":"dc1d7ae267cf27a07142f69a7381ff63743ae42f","tid":214753,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「東」 字依個象形字,  最早出現喺甲骨文<br />\n同 束 字同源,  「東」喺古代,   係一束物品紥成一舊包裹既意思,  以前遠行既人出門就係拎依依個包裹向太陽升起既方向出發 <br />\n<br />\n所以 , 「東」有以下既演變<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.vividict.com/UpFile/5/201006220138235708d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vividict.com%2FUpFile%2F5%2F201006220138235708d.gif&h=74c34c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以係有 「東」先, 而唔係因為「東」家 個「東」先架<br />\n<br />\n樓上 9 up 當秘笈  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023d4b4d2598606a97a636d45a0cd834168752ac","tid":214753,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東＝東家＝主塲＝我話事<br />\n所以就東行先<br />\n<br />\n至於其他就ＷＦＣ</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至於北行最後<br />\n<br />\n因為北有背的意義，例如敗北<br />\n<br />\n&quot;背&quot;係最後面，所以北要行最後</blockquote><br />\n駁吾到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9  up 當秘笈"}]}